1235
01:29:19.492 --> 01:29:21.615
COSMO: All right, Kathy. Go ahead.

1236
01:29:22.370 --> 01:29:24.913
KATHY: Nothing can keep us apart.

1237
01:29:24.914 --> 01:29:28.960
Our love will last till
